This is KingPong project.



With SBT:
=========

Make sure that the Android SDK is present and export its location:

    export ANDROID_SDK_ROOT=/usr/local/Cellar/android-sdk/r21.0.1

Compile and package:

    sbt
    > compile
    > android:package-debug

Launch the emulator, use TAB to see available avd:

    > android:emulator-start TAB

Install KingPong on the device:

    > android:start-emulator

Stop the emulator:

    > android:emulator-stop